  <Strings>
    <Section>Story</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37368</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_180_001</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わたしの大好物のメロン……っと</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'll put my favorite melon here and...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38100</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_180_002</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Mint&gt;の好きなのは、リンゴ、だっけ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, &lt;Mint&gt;, you like apples, right?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38400</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_180_003</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え、ええ……
で、ですが、それは、ちょっと……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>W-Well, yes... However that's...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39172</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_180_004</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……な、なんか焦げくさいぞ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey... I smell something burning...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39540</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_180_005</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>香ばしいの間違いでしょ？
これぞ、&lt;Arche&gt;特製フルーツ焼き！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's a weird way to say "tasty".
Behold, &lt;Arche&gt;'s special grilled fruits!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41160</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_180_006</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ヤバいぞ！　誰か水持ってこい！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This is bad! Someone get the water!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42776</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_180_007</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ふぅ……なんとか
延焼は防げたみたいだ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Phew...We managed to stop the fire
from spreading, somehow...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43124</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_180_008</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Chester&gt;……あんたは……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Chester&gt;, you...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43636</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_180_009</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おまえ、もう少し自分の料理の腕を
自覚した方がいいぞ！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Why the glare? It'd do you some good 
to be more self-aware of your cooking skills.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44264</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_180_010</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……&lt;Mel&gt;のマシュマロ入りカレーと
どっこいどっこいかな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Sheesh...This might be as bad as &lt;Mel&gt;'s
marshmallow curry if not worse.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
